meeting.infoNote:
Times on the text agenda are shown in Vienna local time, UTC +1.
Please see our Meeting FAQ for information about hybrid meetings, COVID-19 preparations and more.
To see information on public side meetings, visit the meeting wiki.
For our social/hallway space, please visit Gather. Password: notewell
For Meetecho resources and tutorials, visit Preparing for IETF 113.
